  "title": "Hyperkalaemia",
  "body_html": "<div>Signs of hyperkalaemia on an ECG are flattened P waves, widened QRS and tall tented T waves.  Untreated it will deteriorate to a sine wave pattern, leading to cardiac arrest.<br />It is difficult to correspond potassium level and ECG changes, the rate of onset of the hyperkalaemia will also influence any ECG changes.<br /><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperkalemia'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399b.png'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">3</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Physiology</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Endocrine physiology</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nSigns of hyperkalaemia on an ECG are flattened P waves, widened QRS and tall tented T waves.  Untreated it will deteriorate to a sine wave pattern, leading to cardiac arrest.<br />It is difficult to correspond potassium level and ECG changes, the rate of onset of the hyperkalaemia will also influence any ECG changes.<br /><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperkalemia'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb399b.png'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br></div>",
